that <HI>Homer</HI> is of this <HI>Opinion</HI> in his <HI>second,</HI>
th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> against it in his <HI>first</HI> Poem. If it be said that
<HI>Reason</HI> is against it, let that <HI>Reason</HI> be produc'd;
