Followers.</P>
<P>The <HI>Language</HI> in which this <HI>Book</HI> was written is
<HI>Hebrew;</HI> and considering the very great <HI>difference</HI>
there is between the <HI>Stil<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> or manner of <HI>Expression</HI> in
the <HI>Eastern</HI> and <HI>Western</HI> part of the World, their <HI>E|loquence,</HI>
as well as their <HI>Customs</HI> and <HI>Habits,</HI> be|ing
