<HI>literal Translation</HI> of this <HI>Book</HI> as 'tis now found in
<PB REF="12">
the <HI>Bible,</HI> especially considering how long time since it
was <HI>written,</HI> how <HI>little</HI> the <HI>Language</HI> is understood,
and how much the <HI>Idiom</HI> of it is lost, should not sound
